Privacy Policy for Hava.co
Hava.co is a purpose-driven company that aims to empower people everywhere to revolutionize their health. Our mission is to make healthy living simple and accessible. By using the Hava.co website, any of our apps, or other services, you agree to the following terms and conditions:
Information We Collect
Personal Data
When you use Hava.co, we may collect and process the following types of personal data:
Identity Data: Includes your name, username, email address, and any other information you provide during account registration or profile creation.
Contact Data: Includes your postal address, telephone number, and other contact details you provide.
Financial Data: Includes payment card details. However, please note that we do not store your payment card details as they are processed directly by our trusted third-party payment providers.
Technical Data: Includes your IP address, device information, operating system, browser type, and other technical information about your use of Hava.co.
Usage Data: Includes information about your interactions with our website, app, and services, such as pages visited, features used, and time spent on the platform.
Marketing and Communications Data: Includes your preferences in receiving marketing communications from us.
Tracking and Cookies
We may use cookies, web beacons, and similar tracking technologies to collect information about your browsing behavior and usage patterns. This helps us improve our services, provide personalized content, and deliver targeted advertisements. You can manage your cookie preferences by adjusting your browser settings. Please refer to our Cookie Policy for more information.
Third-Party Tracking
We may engage third-party service providers to track and analyze user behavior on Hava.co for advertising and service improvement purposes. These providers may use cookies, web beacons, and other tracking technologies to collect data about your interactions with our platform. This data may be used to deliver targeted advertisements based on your interests and preferences. Please refer to the section on "Third-Party Services" for more information.
How We Use Your Information
Provision of Services
We use your personal data to provide you with access to our website, app, and other services. This includes managing your account, processing payments, delivering content, and responding to your inquiries and support requests.
Personalization and Improvements
We may use your information to personalize your experience on Hava.co, such as recommending relevant content and providing customized features. We also analyze user behavior and feedback to improve our services, develop new features, and enhance user satisfaction.
Communication and Marketing
With your consent, we may send you promotional communications about our products, services, and updates. You can opt-out of receiving marketing messages at any time by following the instructions provided in the communications or by contacting us directly.
Legal Compliance and Protection
We may process your personal data to comply with applicable laws, regulations, and legal obligations. We also reserve the right to use your information to protect our rights, property, and safety, as well as the rights, property, and safety of our users and the general public.
Sharing and Disclosure of Information
Third-Party Services
We may share your personal data with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in delivering our services. These providers may include payment processors, hosting providers, analytics providers, advertising partners, and customer support platforms. We ensure that these third parties process your data in accordance with applicable